jCategories...

svn co http://forge.jelix.org/svn/jblog/trunk/jblog/modules/jcategories

HOW TO USE : 

1/ display categories' list 
$this->_tpl->assignZone("categorylist", "jcategories~categorylist");
// or
{zone "jcategories~categorylist"}

2/ get name of a category by its id
$categoryName = $srv_categories->getCategoryNameById($scope, $id);
